  "instructions": "<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>",
  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>U <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Simple Past</span>, pitanja mogu početi sa upitnom reči (npr., <span class=\"highlighted-text\">what</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">where</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">how</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">who</span>) sa sledećim formatom:</p>\n<p><strong>Upitna reč + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">did</span> + Tema + osnovni glagol.</strong></p>\n<p>Pitanje Lise, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">What did you find there?</span>, koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">what</span> da pita za specifične informacije o rezultatima akcija Jamesa. Ostali primeri su:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Where did you go yesterday?</span> - Pitaš o mestu.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">How did they solve the problem?</span> - Pitaš za put.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Who did you call last night?</span> - Pita o osobi.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Tokom razgovora, Lisa pita o otkriću Jamesa dok traže grešku.</p>\n</section>",
